 ubermenu-has-submenu-drop" data-ubermenu-trigger="mouseover" ><a class="ubermenu-target ubermenu-item-layout-default ubermenu-item-layout-text_only" href="https://hobbyfrontline.com/category/premium-bandai/"><span class="ubermenu-target-title ubermenu-target-text">Premium Bandai</span><i class='ubermenu-sub-indicator fas fa-angle-down'></i></a><ul  class="ubermenu-tab-content-panel ubermenu-column ubermenu-column-5-6 ubermenu-submenu ubermenu-submenu-id-4676 ubermenu-submenu-type-tab-content-panel"  ><li id="menu-item-5152" class="ubermenu-item ubermenu-item-type-custom ubermenu-item-object-ubermenu-custom ubermenu-item-5152 ubermenu-item-auto ubermenu-item-header ubermenu-item-level-3 ubermenu-column ubermenu-column-auto" ><div class="ubermenu-content-block ubermenu-custom-content ubermenu-custom-content-padded"><img src="https://hobbyfrontline.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/pb_o.png" width="320" /><br /><br />
<p>Premium Bandai kits are variations of standard kits and are produced in very limited quantities. They are normally only available to consumers in Japan, China, Hong Kong directly from Bandai's web shop, and are not on sale to international customers. We are able to order any item that is currently available for pre-order from Bandai. We can also source most of the previously released items at reasonable prices.</p>
